entries.title: Developer & Designer
entries.description: Here I worked with a team of developers & designers to launch a health & wellness app for parenthood, using a Rust backend and a Python frontend. I aided the company in their 2023 V0 launch and their re-branding to Moment for Parents.

entries.title: Developer
entries.description: Looking for a new challenge, I joined Atomic Object. My role was to join a team of developers and designers in effort to replace a client's entire website tech-stack.

entries.title: Computer Science Summer Institute Intern
entries.description: The spark in my journey to using code and graphics together. After this internship, I was convinced that not only was I good at coding, I could marry it with my passion for art.
